Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的    身为妖精的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要乘坐这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在听吗    诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常惬意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说呢    这样跟战士长一起也很不错哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Queen's  Blade结束后的现如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应该立刻返回妖精森林去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而顺从了诺瓦的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微绕了点远路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实    再坚持一直以来的死板想法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的和长老们没有区别了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让要妖精族的长老们…认同诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士…长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沼地魔女的威胁尚未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这般玩乐的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定妖精之森已经陷入了危机之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长    快来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我认为新女王会去讨伐沼地魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却没有绝对的保证
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也听说过有人在袭击斗士这样的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能太悠闲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事    战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使不上力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从无法好好计算剩余体力这点看来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧要关头时可无法派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    20分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是大海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一次看到海对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会去海边玩玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想想我们绕了多少远路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好宽    好广    好壮丽    大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋    哪有人会裸奔下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且下水前还要先做热身运动才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这水好咸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的海水就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    待在那别动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eagle  Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打偏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把…把这穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西不穿也没关系的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了    这里跟妖精森林的泉水可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论无论如何都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么不听话还真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是休息一晚的话或许也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了    休息一晚对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了明天就出发回妖精森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险    战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不放水的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了斗士名利双收的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会厉害到飞起耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们不需要手下留情    来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电发球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去了    诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了    战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒    好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    70分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗    真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是    战斗还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么呢    这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我必须回妖精森林才行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护妖精森林才是我的使命    是内心的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…是什么呢…这内心的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的幸福与满足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆就这样跟诺瓦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露    没问题    一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了    诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海里有什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长    你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么    不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    那个球是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暗处会隐约发光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧    战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前战士长曾告诉过我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片海底存在着不可思议的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是叫「思念石」来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘…不瞒着战士长就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们运气好过头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊    好的没话说    多到爆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是斗士大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大半夜的搞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道    搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太暗找不到呢    露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不潜下去不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了    诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我靠    「胜利之风」竟然断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶    让它逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的    斗士大人    太谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先别管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思    我正在找我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊    她的话刚刚往岩壁去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩壁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要去那种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的海流会随时间突然改变    超危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且听说魔物经常会在那里出现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是闹着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露    你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露    诺瓦在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那球…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会被魔物给…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等失态    何等怠慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以前的我怎么可能觉察不到魔物的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢妖精族战斗教官的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不该在这种地方悠然自得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明清楚这点却还…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水流好像变缓了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在岛的后方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有湿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退潮后地面露出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可千万别出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露    不好意思    把衣服给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃了东西让身子暖和起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能合你胃口的话就再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃    这是妮库丝小姐做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊    是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是不是因遭到海浪蹂躏的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从海藻中可以煮出不少汤汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐真是厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不    我还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有弗尼库拉大人在我才能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在熟睡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把杖还是丢掉比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给人一种不祥的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直拿着那把杖是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是    没有弗尼库拉大人在我就什么也做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐不是能做出这么好吃的料理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    叫我好找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊    湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想不到你会在这种地方悠闲地吃着东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐请我吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰使妮库丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的魔物是你的把戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐一直跟诺瓦在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物正是那把名为弗尼库拉的杖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝只不过是个被杖给操控了的内心软弱之人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐待人非常亲切    非常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回妖精森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是战士长你全身都湿透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快晒干的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话喝碗热海藻汤再走如何呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你照顾诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我可不想跟魔物打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的使命是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我    吾之徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林的守门人诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩耍的时间已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗尼库拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着    诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦    没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要弄出好汤汁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火候可是比什么都重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不肯吃我这个正义的火焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝大人亲手做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意了    诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个家伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对弗尼库拉大人说这说那的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上是想从我身边夺走弗尼库拉大人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的    诺瓦我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是在重复单调的攻击而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间长了自然会露出破绽的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时便是取胜的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并非你自身的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟连其是邪恶魔物之力都觉察不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰哩八嗦    叽叽歪歪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰仗弗尼库拉大人又有何错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟因此就能变强    老娘是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲    没有依靠就无法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurricane  Fury
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长    小心背后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗尼库拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要你的明明是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是想对我进行附体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心灵正被逐渐侵蚀…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我难道今后想活下去就必须要有所依靠了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦…诺瓦…诺瓦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我… 放开战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗尼库拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐    其实大家都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的话会感到孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不依靠别人就无法生活下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是    总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要独立的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终将会来临的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗尼库拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮库丝小姐…走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了我不会游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我    拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从在妖精森林跟诺瓦相遇起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止我总是优先考虑诺瓦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是认为诺瓦还需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是我需要着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要任何话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定跟妮库丝一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都无法独自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不依靠别人就无法生活下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:22:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要独立的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终将会来临的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在此说再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回到森林的话会给我带去麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有这方面的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.99,0:23:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不全是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家相遇后我才发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾基多娜小姐也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Queen's  Blade中遇到的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不依赖着他人而独立生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想一个人看看更为广阔的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从何时起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就开始这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这次的旅途之中下定的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最后我想把这个送给战士长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:23:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手中将其握热就能见到最为思念之人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前战士长跟我这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…还记得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我开始搜集石头的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且战士长说过的话诺瓦是绝不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好不容易才找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却摔坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有这种石头
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有这种石头…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也绝对不会忘记你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经活了超过千年的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.42,0:24:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.54,0:24:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你在一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.70,0:24:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是任何事物也无法取代的美好回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.51,0:24:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.25,0:24:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经成长的如此出色了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有任何东西可以教给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.41,0:25:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.50,0:25:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.44,0:25:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瓦啊    已经没有东西可以束缚你了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.85,0:25:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始就用你的眼睛、耳朵和心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.31,0:25:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去好好感悟更多更多的事物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.57,0:25:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这广袤的世界一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.02,0:25:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填满你的好奇心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.01,0:25:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.42,0:25:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时我们再在某处重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.40,0:25:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前便先告别了    诺瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.08,0:25:54.47,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\an8}不胜依依艾琳千年别离
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.18,0:27:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳…还以为我要领便当了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.66,0:27:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个死妖精真叫人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.94,0:27:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…弗…弗尼库拉大人
